  <entry>
    <title>Intellectual Property Right</title>
    <link href="http://deepcreator.com/2018/04/13/IPR/Intellectual%20Property%20Right/"/>
    <id>http://deepcreator.com/2018/04/13/IPR/Intellectual Property Right/</id>
    <published>2018-04-13T11:28:08.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-04-13T11:51:36.577Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://p53s4d2qk.bkt.clouddn.com/intellectualpropertyright20180413.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/!75p" alt="intellectualpropertyright20180413.jpg"></p><blockquote><p><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E4%BA%A7%E6%9D%83/85044?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">权利人对其智力劳动所创作的成果享有的财产权利</a>。</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="基础概念"><a href="#基础概念" class="headerlink" title="基础概念"></a>基础概念</h2><p><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UGpQA9V7jqw4ABDxB3c-5Q" target="_blank" rel="noopener">原来搞懂知识产权这么简单！ </a></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3LRf3ViaZiatZAlc0QyoQiafHAJjWERcw3AhbTJiahIK4piaav4iaib91gP2Jcib1GjTYiccIfWSKzZAulX4XO8ynzBpEoA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" alt=""><br>知识产权的实质是把人类的智力成果作为财产来看待。<br>知识产权包括<strong>工业产权</strong>和<strong>版权（著作权）</strong>两个部分</p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3LRf3ViaZiatZAlc0QyoQiafHAJjWERcw3AzYE6SEcX0gPEia7rVq6JcLibo1MKxjvp9SQT7ibCnJOMDzfwwrhHrXOPA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" alt=""><br>工业产权包括专利、商标、服务标志、厂商名称、原产地名称，以及植物新品种权和集成电路布图设计专有权等。</p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3LRf3ViaZiatZAlc0QyoQiafHAJjWERcw3ApvBFhzOLhufh0HEjQAoLGiaKkZQtYBNTO74b2rg4DuWIxAYITm8GhFQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" alt=""><br>版权即著作权，是指文学、艺术、科学作品的作者对其作品享有的权利（包括财产权、人身权）。<br>计算机软件著作权，行业内简称“软著”，计算机软件著作权是指软件的开发者或者其他权利人依据有关著作权法律的规定，对于软件作品所享有的各项专有权利。</p><h3 id="时间期限"><a href="#时间期限" class="headerlink" title="时间期限"></a>时间期限</h3><p>生命留给我们的时间是有限的<br>同样的<br>果汁局留给申请人/代理人的<a href="http://www.patexplorer.com/txmessage/detail.html?id=86" target="_blank" rel="noopener">时间</a>也不多！</p><p><img src="http://p53s4d2qk.bkt.clouddn.com/iprtimelimit20180413.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/!75p" alt="iprtimelimit20180413.jpg"></p><h2 id="海报赏析"><a href="#海报赏析" class="headerlink" title="海报赏析"></a><a href="http://ip.people.com.cn/GB/391947/391952/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">海报赏析</a></h2><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311101000222932991817.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>尊重知识</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311111000097039117941.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>崇尚创新</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311112000343831627387.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>诚信守法</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311113000032865579176.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>行动一起来</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111651000155029024660.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>以道治盗</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111649000392038573151.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>走自己的路</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111650000267903221224.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>给原创一个支点</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111648000249478557151.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>传播创新的种子</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111647000281150759842.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>创与盗</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111642000136920292442.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>尊重原创 恪守己道</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111644000133059303981.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>尊重知识·崇尚创新·诚信守法</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111640000364787085572.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>镜以明盗</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111638000596907125993.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>模仿再像，也吃不了虫子</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111636000014464872181.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>点亮原创之灯</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2015/0811/MAIN201508111626000332142144058.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>因乐而动 为乐维权</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311119000383401386683.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>做自己，飞得更远</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311118000375865477969.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>中国制造到中国创造</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311116000309508682606.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>化蝶</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://ip.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2014/1231/MAIN201412311113000363488890491.jpg" alt=""></p><blockquote><p>保护</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://p53s4d2qk.bkt.clouddn.com/intellectualpropertyright20180413.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/!75p&quot; alt=&quot;intellectualpropertyright20180413.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E4%BA%A7%E6%9D%83/85044?fr=aladdin&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;权利人对其智力劳动所创作的成果享有的财产权利&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
